    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pazelletee juhțaß Azzis\nprett Debbefim/ un uſtraugajt\nto Semmi appakscha/ jo ta Deb-\nbes iſnihks ka Dulymi/ un ta\nSemme nodils ka kahda Dreḫ-\nbe/ un winnas Eedsihwotaj ne-\nmirs ka fcha. Bet manna Pe-\nſtischana buhs muhſchiga/ man-\nna Taifniba ne fakritihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufajt man/ juhs/ kas\njuhs Taifnibu paſibſtat/ juhs\nLaudis/ kam manna Bauſliba\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Girdi irr. Ne bibſteetes par to\nZilwekn Neewafchani/ un ne\niſbihſtaces preeſch winno Sat-\nmoſchanahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Kuſtoni tohs ehdihſ ka\nkahdu Dreḫbi/ un Kohdas apeh-\nidhs tohs ka Willu/ bet manna\nTaifniba buhs muhſchiga/ un\nmanma Peſtischana us Zilſchu\nZiltim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uſmohſtees/ uſmohſtees/\napwelz Stiprumu/ tu Elkons\nta KUNGGA/ uſmohſtees ka\nwezzôs Laikds muhſcham. Woj\ntu ne eſti tas/ kas to Lepno irr\niſzirtis/ un to Puhki irr eewai-\nnijs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Woj tu ne eſſitas patę/\nkas to Juhrn ta leela Beſdibbi-\nna Uhdeni irr iſkaltejs? kas tohs\nJuhras Dſittumus irr par wee-\nnu Zettu darrijs/ ka tee Atpeſti-\ntee zaur gahje?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tä atgreesiſees tee Atpe-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es/ es eſmu tas/ juh\nEepreezinatajs/ kas eſſi tu/\ntu preeſch Zilwekeem bibſtee\nkam jamirſt? un preeſch Zilu-\nku Behrneem/ kas ka See\ntohp turreti?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un aſemirſti to KUNG-\ntawu Darritaju/ kas to Debb\niſplattijs/ un to Semmi dib-\nnajs? un tu bibſtees bes Mit-\nſchanas zauru Deenu no ta\nBahrsibas ta Apbehdinataj\nkad tas taifahs maitaht; Kur\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas/ kas Swetchu-\nzeetinahts irr/taps ahtri iſlais\nun Bedre ne nomirs/ un win-\nMatsf winnam ne truhks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es eſmu tas KUNG-\ntaws Deews/ kas to Juhrn\nſtina/ ka winnas Wilni kan\nKUNGGS Zebaot irr wi-\nWahrds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es leeſu man-\nWahrdus tavā Muttē/ un\nflabju teewi appakſch man-\nRohkas Ehnaę/ ka es to Deb-\nſi dehſtiju/ un to Semmi dib-\nnajn/ un us Ziann fakka : Ju-\neſſat manni Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uſmohſtees/ uſmohſtee-\nzellees Jeruſaleme/ kas tu no-\nKUNGGA Rohkas eſſi oſeh-\n"
    }
  ],
